	<name>TuxScape2</name>
	<summary>SpaceTux adventure</summary>
	<description>
		<p>Explore Space.</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Scroll = Zoom Camera.</li>
			<li>Mouse Move = Rotate Camera &amp; Ship Direction.</li>
			<li>W,A,S,D / Arrow Keys = Fly/Move Directions.</li>
			<li>Right Click = Hold for free look camera.</li>
			<li>Space / Shift = Up and Down altitude.</li>
			<li>E = Steal Nearby Ship.</li>
			<li>C = Change FOV.</li>
			<li>R = Reset game.</li>
			<li>F = FPS to console.</li>
		</ul>
	</description>
